snippet.title: Island of Winds Gameplay Trailer | PC Gaming Show: Most Wanted 2024
snippet.description:
Island of Winds is an adventure game set in the 17th century, in which you explore an Icelandic landscape, using magic to solve puzzles and unveil main character Byrnhildur’s complex, emotional past.
